{"tid":401803,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 8上台出機月費貴到呢⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-09-16T02:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T07:15:45.000Z","uid":52078,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e431481e8a2e6f53af2c192be3dfc50efa72c2","tid":401803,"uid":52078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"iPhone 8 同plus都網上任買，仲上台出機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/102812_d7795f9709be73922f4d672cb7aa962d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F102812_d7795f9709be73922f4d672cb7aa962d.jpg&h=cd7274c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus 15日在官網正式開賣，各大電訊商亦針對各位準備上台出新iPhone的用家，推出不同的上台出機月費計劃。所有電訊商都要求簽約24個月，並收需增值服務費及隧道費。TOPick比較後發現SmarTone出價最進取。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1905399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1905399&d=2eCDVJIknrktphmt0Xw3UjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=eb1f0069\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1905399</a><br />\n<br />\niPhone 8上台月費計劃出爐: csl.<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2x9v5t5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2x9v5t5&d=2eCDVJIknrktphmt0Xw3UjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=dff19488\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2x9v5t5</a><br />\niPhone 8上台月費計劃出爐:1010<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2fplogE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2fplogE&d=2eCDVJIknrktphmt0Xw3UjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=70d4df82\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2fplogE</a><br />\niPhone 8上台月費計劃出爐:SmarTone<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2wi2H94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wi2H94&d=2eCDVJIknrktphmt0Xw3UjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA